o join your colony. Then, put your colonists to work on advanced facilities used to create complex goods, defend against hostile aliens, and perform other advanced functions such as terraforming and power generation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2810070/extras/0f90ebc661a5f201e456fd6403449281.poster.avif?t=1746194372\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2810070/extras/0f90ebc661a5f201e456fd6403449281.webm?t=1746194372\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2810070/extras/0f90ebc661a5f201e456fd6403449281.mp4?t=1746194372\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Things Are Warming Up</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Once you begin terraforming the planet, ice melts, giving you access to new areas. Here, you will find more advanced materials used to advance the terraforming process.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2810070/extras/2b768fe339349e8c1ebf5bf0b1fd977a.poster.avif?t=1746194372\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2810070/extras/2b768fe339349e8c1ebf5bf0b1fd977a.webm?t=1746194372\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2810070/extras/2b768fe339349e8c1ebf5bf0b1fd977a.mp4?t=1746194372\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Defend Your Assets</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As terraforming advances, you will need to defend yourself against attacks from hostile alien creatures on the ground and in the air.  Eventually, you will take the fight to them by destroying alien nests and going on expeditions to eliminate all hostile life forms to make Ceres safe for humanity.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2810070/extras/ad303b40109c4a3efacb7639a4e34eab.poster.avif?t=1746194372\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2810070/extras/ad303b40109c4a3efacb7639a4e34eab.webm?t=1746194372\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2810070/extras/ad303b40109c4a3efacb7639a4e34eab.mp4?t=1746194372\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The higher the difficulty settings combined with how quickly you complete milestones or the terraforming of Ceres will determine how well you score on the leaderboards.  Can you be efficient and reach the top spot?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>So what are you waiting for?  Get in there and start terraforming the dwarf planet Ceres into a viable human colony today.</i></p>",
